= General =
For meetings, we use Evo Online. Please register for an Evo account well in advance, as it can take up to 24 hours to register.
= Agenda =
If you wish to add items to the Agenda for the upcoming meeting, please propose them here: [[LibSBGN/MeetingAgenda|MeetingAgenda]]
